[{"Code":"en","Title":"Testing xenPlatform features","Slug":"testing-xenplatform-features","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"md6vnkkm-51tnol-007\">Sub-accounts can be created while your master account is still in <a href=\"/docs/your-dashboard\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Test Mode</a>. Test sub-accounts allow you to create mock transactions using your test API key and see the transactions appear on your dashboard in Test Mode. With xenPlatform activated, you can also simulate routing payments between accounts.</p><p data-block-id=\"md6vnkkm-51tnol-007\">Note that there are some functions that are not available in Test Mode:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"866\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:866px;width:866px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:383px;\"><col style=\"width:226px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"md6vpbrg-buzikq-009\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63uku-e45600-001\">Available in Test Mode</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63uku-3y481p-002\">Available in Live Mode</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm65r9e-6j9our-010\">Create any sub-account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm660gm-wgvhmk-013\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm6669j-sir7ik-016\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67jrx-o6u5ey-0