roup><col style=\"width:383px;\"><col style=\"width:226px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"md6vpbrg-buzikq-009\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63uku-e45600-001\">ใช้งานได้ใน Test Mode</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63uku-3y481p-002\">ใช้งานได้ใน Live Mode</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm65r9e-6j9our-010\">สร้างบัญชีย่อยใด ๆ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm660gm-wgvhmk-013\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm6669j-sir7ik-016\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67jrx-o6u5ey-028\">การเข้าสู่ระบบบัญชีย่อย</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67tnu-mqygh5-032\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67qy6-lrh31d-030\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td 