d=\"mfm66si8-oy6hl3-022\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm66yrp-g261ab-023\">การชำระเงิน, Split และ Transfers</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67bp6-dn8hy0-024\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67bp6-xjkqxv-025\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67crv-wy7hyi-027\">Account Holder API (Legacy)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm68a5g-3zag03-033\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm68a5g-59hijp-034\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"md6vnkkm-51tnol-007\"></p>","SeoTitle":"การทดสอบฟีเจอร์ xenPlatform","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Probando funcionalidades de xenPlatform","Slug":"testing-xenplatform-features","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"md6vnkkm-51tnol-007\">Las subcuentas pueden crearse mientras su cuenta maestra aún se encuentra en <a href=\"/docs/your-dashboard\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Test Mode</a>. Las subcuentas de prueba le permiten crear transacciones simuladas utilizando su API key de prueba y ver las transacciones aparecer en su dashboard en Test Mode. Con xenPlatform activado, también puede simular el enrutamiento de Payments entre cuentas.</p><p data-block-id=\"md6vnkkm-51tnol-007\">Tenga en cuenta que hay algunas funciones que no están disponibles en Test Mode:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"866\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:866px;width:866px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:383px;\"><col style=\"width:226px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"md6vpbrg-buzikq-009\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63uku-e45600-001\">Disponible en Test Mode</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63uku-3y481p-002\">Disponible en Live Mode</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm65r9e-6j9our-010\">Crear cualquier subcuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm660gm-wgvhmk-013\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"