></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm63ukv-gvynaa-008\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm65ql9-x8yfgo-009\">Verificar subcuentas usando el API <code>/account_verification</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm66roo-0qs30t-020\">Solo tipo <code>OWNED</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm66si8-oy6hl3-022\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm66yrp-g261ab-023\">Payments, Split y Transferencias</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67bp6-dn8hy0-024\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67bp6-xjkqxv-025\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"383\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm67crv-wy7hyi-027\">Account Holder API (Legacy)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"226\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:;border-color:;vertical-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm68a5g-3zag03-033\"><emoji data-name=\"